---
<section class="py-20 px-6 bg-slate-800" id="comparison">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-16">
      從「人肉爬樓」到<span class="text-blue-400">「智能快篩」</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl p-8 border-2 border-slate-700">
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
          <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg mb-4">
            傳統人工 QA
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 text-slate-400">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mt-1 text-slate-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-lg">每天只能爬 50 則對話紀錄</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 text-slate-400">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mt-1 text-slate-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-lg">發現客訴時通常已過 3 天</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 text-slate-400">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mt-1 text-slate-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-lg">難以判斷「是否有溫度的回覆」</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900/30 to-purple-900/30 rounded-xl p-8 border-2 border-blue-500/50">
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
          <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 text-white rounded-lg font-bold text-lg mb-4">
            Pureteatime AI
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 text-blue-200">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mt-1 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium">每秒分析 1,000+ 則訊息</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 text-blue-200">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mt-1 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium">負面關鍵字 0.1 秒即時通報</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 text-blue-200">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mt-1 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium">量化「同理心」與「解決率」指標</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

